Comment: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:32.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:42.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:45.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:57.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:02.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:17.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:22.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:27.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:32.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:36.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:51.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:51.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
